Title : The Brook, Nelson
Text : {{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}
'''The Brook''' is one of the suburbs of [[Nelson, New Zealand]]. It lies to the south of Nelson and is the location of the [[Brook Waimarama Sanctuary]], a conservation project at the head of the Brook Valley.<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/nelson-mail/features/weekend/8608227/The-two-sides-of-the-fence | title=Two Sides of the Fence | work=Stuff.co.nz | date=29 April 2013 | accessdate=2 May 2014 | author=Arnold, Naomi}}</ref>

The population was 1401 in the [[New Zealand census|2013 census]]. This was an increase of 237 people since the 2006 Census.<ref>{{NZ Quickstats2013|14602|The Brook}}</ref>

